<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Author Request - Orbit Blog</title>
    <style>
      /* General Reset */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #eaeaea;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        margin: 0;
        color: #c026d3;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email-body h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-top: 0;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .email-footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #999;
        padding: 10px;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #c026d3;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #aaa;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1><%=siteName%></h1>
      </div>

      <div class="email-body">
        <h2>Hello <%= name %>,</h2>
        <p>
          We are thrilled to inform you that your request to become an author on
          <strong><%=siteName%></strong> has been approved!
        </p>
        <p>
          As an author, you now have access to your author dashboard, where you
          can create, edit, and manage your posts. We are excited to see your
          contributions to our platform and share your unique voice with our
          audience.
        </p>
        <p>
          To get started, click the button below to log in to your dashboard:
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: center">
          <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="btn">Go to Dashboard</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out
          to us. Weâ€™re here to support you every step of the way.
        </p>
        <p>
          Happy blogging!<br />
          The <%=siteName%> Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> <%=siteName%>. All rights
          reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
